Computer Shopper - November 2010
PDF | 172 pages | English 
Computer Shopper - the UK's biggest technology magazine.
Computer Shopper puts you in a great position to negotiate when buying anything to do with PCs. Every issue features more industry advertisers then any other PC magazine. So you can compare prices quickly and easily, to make sure you get the best deal.
